WEBVTT

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.840
"You have cancer."

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:13.120
Sadly, about 40 percent of us will hear
those three words within our lifetime,

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:15.960
and half will not survive.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:20.816
This means that two out of five
of your closest friends and relatives

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:23.296
will be diagnosed
with some form of cancer,

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:24.800
and one will die.

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:28.736
Beyond the physical hardships,

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.936
roughly one-third
of cancer survivors here in the US